	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cannibalize is the key to shammy soloing.<br><br>Cast regen on yourself, always. Then when your medding watch your mana bar, the moment you see it increase stand up cast regen and *as soon* as you recover click the med button again. This will make sure you have the maximum regen of HP and mana as possible. <br><br>At lvl 30 I was soloing Tarzaks in the Great divide. Casting affliction on them, running (having already regened and sowed myself) casting root then, while they're rooted cast envemoned breath, med and do the canni thing as much as possible. If root breaks run and wait until they're far enough away and cast root again. Refresh the dots when need be. <br><br>Hope this helps.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
